<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Butter2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Butter,</orth> vb., to smear with butter; to cook with butter: <cit><quote>I'll have my brains ta'en out and --ed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 5, 8</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>--ed his hay,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 2.4.127" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 4, 127</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>eat no fish of fortune's --ing,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 5.2.9" default="NO" valid="yes">All's V, 2, 9</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>